explanation: [0-0] A woman with short, off-white hair, wearing a purple hooded sweatshirt with "BALENCIAGA" printed in white, stands behind a phone mounted on a stand, raising one finger. To her right is a person in green clothing, both hands pointing downwards. On the white wall behind them are images of seven dance moves and a green monster head.
[0-2] The woman grooves to the music, waving one finger in front of her a few times, sticking out her tongue and smiling. Then she winks with a grin, making a finger-gun gesture.

[2-11] Following the music, the woman imitates the dance moves behind her. When a white check mark with a green background appears under a specific move, she performs it. The person in green next to her mirrors her movements. The woman sways her body back and forth while dancing. She grins while performing the first four moves, and pouts during the fifth and sixth. The rightmost move gradually descends, covering the green monster head. As the woman mirrors this, her mouth twists to the left.
